item.title: 【Music Videos】PACK - Aaliyah Music Videos
item.description:
Blackground had their record label defunct for a while and idk if they have all of their multimedia in the best quality. I tried sourcing them from the best qualities that I could find, and wrote a sharpness algorithm to check if the video itself was enlarged but the pixels were just stretched instead of actually having better resolution/clarity. Sourced from Blackground's YT, Tidal, DVD .vobs, random uploads, and sometimes remastered projects. This is mostly for AI enhancement restoration projects and collectors
